OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FBy ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FThe Scottish finance minister has
OL,10,Fannounced severe cuts to the country's
OL,11,Fpublic services, saying the current
OL,12,Ffinancial situation is "not
OL,13,Fsustainable".
OL,15,FShona Robison announced up to #500
OL,16,Fmillion worth of cuts, including #188
OL,17,Fmillion to be found across government
OL,18,Fdepartments, saying: "I must take
OL,19,Ffurther and more urgent action now to
OL,20,Fmake sure we can balance the Scottish
OL,21,Fbudget."
