OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FThat included #115.8 million of
OL,7,Fsavings from the health and social
OL,8,Fcare budget, but in a letter to MSPs
OL,9,Fon Holyrood's Finance Committee,
OL,10,FRobison offered "assurances that the
OL,11,Fhealth portfolio will seek to protect
OL,12,Fkey frontline emergency services".
OL,14,FThe government also plans to cut
OL,15,Factive travel funding and repurpose
OL,16,Fmoney from other projects to save #65
OL,17,Fmillion, on top of around #60 million
OL,18,Fsaved through spending controls
OL,19,Falready announced.
