OL,6,FRobison said that on top of the
OL,7,F"direct savings" she would make, up to
OL,8,F#460 million from the ScotWind leasing
OL,9,Fround - the process by which Scotland
OL,10,Fleases its seabed to companies wanting
OL,11,Fto build offshore wind farms - will
OL,12,Falso be used, but with the hope it
OL,13,Fwouldn't all need to be spent.
OL,15,F"It is not what I would want to be
OL,16,Fdoing," Robison said when questioned
OL,17,Fon why ScotWind funds were being
OL,18,Futilised.
