OL,6,FRobison did not outline any changes to
OL,7,Ftaxation, but hinted that the Scottish
OL,8,Fgovernment would not increase income
OL,9,Ftax at the next Scottish Budget.
OL,11,FShe highlighted that raising
OL,12,Fsignificant funds from additional
OL,13,Ftaxation would be challenging because
OL,14,Fit would involved "substantial reform"
OL,15,Fto the tax system or further
OL,16,Fdevolution of powers.
