OL,3,CScottish parliament announces #500
OL,4,Cmillion spending cuts
OL,6,FRobison sought to blame Westminster
OL,7,Ffor a "whole new era of austerity"
OL,8,Fboth ahead of and during her update
OL,9,Ffor MSPs on the scale of Scottish
OL,10,Fgovernment spending cuts.
OL,12,F"Were Scotland an independent country
OL,13,Fwe would not be paying the price for
OL,14,Fbad decisions made at Westminster,"
OL,15,FRobison said on Tuesday.
OL,17,FTuesday's speech came ahead of the
OL,18,Ffull Scottish Budget which is set for
OL,19,FDecember 4.
